:(2)推動反貪腐法案。
:(3)罷免支持陳水扁的立法委員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_6070000/newsid_6072500/6072568.stm|title=倒扁運動將推動“公民抗命”|publisher=BBC|date=2016-10-21|accessdate=2015-01-05|archive-date=2015-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105024247/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_6070000/newsid_6072500/6072568.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

